notes: PLEASE ALLOW A 4-6 HOUR TURNAROUND (MAY BE LONGER DURING HIGH VOLUME TIMES). ORDERS PLACED AFTER 3PM FOR PICK-UP AND 12PM FOR DELIVERY MAY GET FILLED THE NEXT DAY, DEPENDING ON ORDER VOLUME. We’re doing our best for our community, however please note there are high labor costs associated with this service. Please consider picking up curb-side (or sending a friend/neighbor to pick up) to minimize charges if that’s important for you.
